item.title: I dont have a item with bonus change?
item.dc:creator: @r3d_th3m3 r3d_th3m3
item.description:
@r3d_th3m3 wrote:

Open up Item.cfg w/notepad
use ctrl + f to find the item you want.
then you will see a lot of numbers.
They will be like.
13000 13000 13000 10 10 10 10 10 10 10 10 10 10 10
Well go to the very end. -----------------------^-^
Those 2 change the str bonus and prayer bonus.
All the others change the defence and attack bonus
